    Tree Arithmetic with Phylogenetic Flows

    Extract pfp object from pfc, the paths of each flow from root to terminal node.

    pf_path.Rd

    Extract pfp object from pfc, the paths of each flow from root to terminal node.

    Usage

    pf_path(x)

    Arguments

    x

    A pfc object

    Value

    A pfp object

    Examples

    pf_path(rpfc(100))
